## Math Engine itex2MML

[itex2MML](https://golem.ph.utexas.edu/~distler/blog/itex2MML.html) converts TeX math formulas into
MathML and can be used together with the [HTML converter](../converter/html.html).

To use itex2MML, set the option ['math_engine'](../options.html#option-math-engine) to 'itex2mml'
and make sure that itex2MML is available. The itex2MML library can be installed, e.g., via Rubygems
by running `gem install itextomml`.

The itex2MML library is released under a triple license: GPL, MPL and LGPL.
